1. Build Instructions
===============================================================================
WARNING: Clean will delete all files under the db directory.

Before beginning please create your properties file under src/main/filters/<username>.properties.
1.1 Please build and install graphical dependency first:

1. cd <project.home>/graphics
2. mvn clean install

1.2 Next generate resources required to run:

1. cd <project.home>/website/main
2. mvn clean process-resources generate-resources

2. Running Instructions
===============================================================================
1. Ensure resources are generated before running (see Build Instructions 1.1 &
   1.2 above)
2. cd <project.home>/website/main
3. mvn grails:run-app


3. Databases
===============================================================================
1. Hypersonic

2. Mysql-----------------------------------------------------------------------
1. Start with mysqld_safe --user=<username> &
2. Start mysql
3. Create database: CREATE DATABASE lsd; (You can remove previous by DROP DATABASE lsd;)
4. Grant permissions: GRANT ALL ON lsd.* TO 'your_mysql_name'@'your_client_host';
